snippet.title: Hot Wheels Unleashed™ Pre-Order Trailer
snippet.description:
Tons of cars from the Hot Wheels™universe, interactive environments where you build insane tracks, and exciting races for you and your friends. The craziest game of the year is coming! Pre-order now your copy of #HotWheelsUnleashed and get ready for Pure Racing Fun.
https://hotwheelsunleashed.com/buy
